{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">验证小球碰撞前后动量守恒。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">动量守恒定律。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">桌子、斜槽、小球、白纸、复写纸</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.点击开始，释放小球，小球落在复写纸上；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.点击重置，并点击斜槽底端的小球，将底端小球放好；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.点击开始，释放小球，顶端小球滑下后撞击底端小球，一起下落到复写纸上；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4.点击显示，拿起白纸，在属性中查看两球质量，根据纸上小球落点验证动量是否守恒。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">如果满足</span></span></span><em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">m</span></em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><sub>1</sub></span><em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">x<sub>OP</sub>=m</span></em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><sub>1</sub></span><em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">x<sub>OM</sub>+m</span></em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><sub>2</sub></span><em><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">x<sub>O&#39;N</sub></span></em><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，则小球碰撞过程动量守恒</span></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">斜槽末端的切线要水平，以保证小球作平抛运动；入射小球的质量要大于被碰小球的质量；入射球在斜槽轨道上的释放点每次都相同；白纸铺好后不能移动。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}